<script>
let PRODUCTS = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('mf_products')||'[]');
let CART = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('mf_cart')||'{}');
const app = document.getElementById('app');
const main = document.getElementById('mainContent');

function formatPrice(num){ return num.toLocaleString('ar-EG') + ' جنيه'; }
function saveProducts(){ localStorage.setItem('mf_products', JSON.stringify(PRODUCTS)); }
function saveCart(){ localStorage.setItem('mf_cart', JSON.stringify(CART)); }
function makePlaceholder(text){ const w=800,h=600,bg='#0b1220',fg='#ffd166'; const svg=`<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='${w}' height='${h}' viewBox='0 0 ${w} ${h}'><rect width='100%' height='100%' fill='${bg}'/><text x='50%' y='50%' fill='${fg}' font-size='48' font-family='Arial' text-anchor='middle' dominant-baseline='central'>${text}</text></svg>`; return 'data:image/svg+xml;utf8,'+encodeURIComponent(svg);}
function escapeXml(s){ return (s+'').replace(/[&<>"']/g,function(c){return {'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;',"'":'&apos;'}[c];}); }

function showStore(){
  main.innerHTML=`<section><div class='grid'></div></section>`;
  const grid = main.querySelector('.grid');
  for(const p of PRODUCTS){
    const card = document.createElement('div'); card.className='product';
    card.innerHTML=`<div class='thumb'><img src='${p.img}' style='width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:8px'></div><div class='info'><div class='name'>${p.name}</div><div class='cat'>${p.category}</div><div class='price'>${formatPrice(p.price)}</div></div>`;
    grid.appendChild(card);
  }
}

function showAdmin(){
  main.innerHTML=`<div class='admin-page'><h2>لوحة إدارة المتجر</h2>
  <h3>إضافة منتج جديد</h3>
  <input id='newName' placeholder='اسم المنتج'/>
  <input id='newCategory' placeholder='الفئة'/>
  <input id='newPrice' type='number' placeholder='السعر'/>
  <textarea id='newDesc' placeholder='وصف المنتج'></textarea>
  <input id='newImg' type='file' accept='image/*'/>
  <button id='addProduct'>إضافة المنتج</button>
  <h3>المنتجات الحالية</h3><div class='admin-grid' id='adminGrid'></div></div>`;
  renderAdminProducts();
  document.getElementById('addProduct').onclick=function(){
    const name=document.getElementById('newName').value;
    const cat=document.getElementById('newCategory').value;
    const price=Number(document.getElementById('newPrice').value);
    const desc=document.getElementById('newDesc').value;
    const file=document.getElementById('newImg').files[0];
    if(!name||!cat||!price||!file){ alert('اكمل جميع الحقول'); return;}
    const reader=new FileReader();
    reader.onload=function(e){
      PRODUCTS.push({id:Date.now(),name,category:cat,price,desc,img:e.target.result}); saveProducts(); renderAdminProducts(); showStore();
    };
    reader.readAsDataURL(file);
  };
}

function renderAdminProducts(){
  const grid=document.getElementById('adminGrid'); grid.innerHTML='';
  for(const p of PRODUCTS){
    const div=document.createElement('div'); div.className='admin-item';
    div.innerHTML=`<div class='admin-thumb'><img src='${p.img}' style='width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px'></div>
    <div style='flex:1'><input value='${p.name}' class='editName'/><input value='${p.category}' class='editCat'/><input type='number' value='${p.price}' class='editPrice'/><textarea class='editDesc'>${p.desc}</textarea>
    <button class='saveBtn'>حفظ</button> <button class='delBtn'>حذف</button></div>`;
    grid.appendChild(div);
    div.querySelector('.saveBtn').onclick=function(){
      p.name=div.querySelector('.editName').value;
      p.category=div.querySelector('.editCat').value;
      p.price=Number(div.querySelector('.editPrice').value);
      p.desc=div.querySelector('.editDesc').value;
      saveProducts(); renderAdminProducts();
    };
    div.querySelector('.delBtn').onclick=function(){
      if(confirm('هل تريد حذف هذا المنتج؟')){ PRODUCTS=PRODUCTS.filter(x=>x.id!==p.id); saveProducts(); renderAdminProducts(); }
    };
  }
}

document.getElementById('goAdmin').onclick=showAdmin;
showStore();
</script>
